&lt;li&gt;Operate at both the micro and macro level. Identifying trends, challenges, and untapped growth opportunities across the organization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dive into large, complex datasets using tools such as SQL, LLMs, Python etc. to break down ambiguous problems and uncover insights and root causes. Transform raw data into clear, actionable recommendations that drive strategy and unlock growth opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and execute high impact projects that improve operational efficiency and unlock new revenue streams. Partner closely with Business Development teams to roll out scalable, repeatable solutions that deliver measurable results.&lt;/li&gt;
