&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;This is a hands-on, builder role for someone who understands both the human side of creator relationships and the data side of content performance. You will move fast, operate with high autonomy, and have direct visibility into how your work shapes the product.&lt;/p&gt;
