&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build Automation Frameworks:&lt;/strong&gt; Design, develop, and maintain scalable automated test suites across APIs and user interfaces to accelerate our regression testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ensure End to End Quality:&lt;/strong&gt; Perform deep functional, integration, and performance testing on core services supporting media processing, high concurrency content delivery, and real time social features.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Quality at Speed:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner closely with developers and product managers to catch bugs early in the development lifecycle, enabling rapid MVP releases without sacrificing platform stability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Guard Platform Integrity &amp;amp; UX:&lt;/strong&gt; Validate content ecosystem safety mechanisms, notification systems, and real time engagement features including messaging and live interactions to guarantee an intuitive, high quality user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimize QA Infrastructure:&lt;/strong&gt; Continually improve our testing tools, environments, and CI/CD integration to enhance overall engineering efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
